sity is necessary\",\"eval\": \"rubric:std-crit-design\"}],\"prose_notes\": \"Experiment: 104 questions; k=5; use m=5 critics with different prompting strategies; measure pairwise error correlation; test majority-rule veto. Confirm: (1) rho < 1; (2) ensemble beats SC; (3) no single critic matches.\"}",
